# ============================================================================
# Poker44 model repo (POKER44_MODEL_REPO_URL) — PRIVACY WHITELIST
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Publish ONLY the trained model artifact and the code needed to run it.
# Everything else stays private: the training pipeline (train_bump.py,
# retrain.py, fetch_benchmark.py), benchmark data/, .env secrets, and the
# rest of the subnet fork.
#
# Strategy: ignore everything, then re-include just the allowed paths.
# ============================================================================

# 1) Ignore everything by default
*

# 2) Keep the git config files themselves
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes

# 3) The trained model artifact
!models/
models/*
!models/bump_model.joblib

# 4) The model "run" package — needed to unpickle and run the model
!poker44_bump/
!poker44_bump/**

# 5) Never publish caches or secrets, even under an un-ignored path above
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.env
.env*
